                  </origin>
                  <provenance>Copied for Walda Pētros ወልደ፡ ጴጥሮስ, fol. 161r; Sold by Ato Waldayyas Delnaśśāhu አቶ፡ ወልደየስ ድልነሣሁ to Makāna Śellāsē Church on 29 Ṭeqemt 1936 EC (9 November 1943), fol. 1v, 4v; Seal of Qeddest Śellāsē Cathedral, fol. 3r. In Trinity Cathedral when filmed.</provenance>
               </history>
